The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Footballer held

Rajkot: A former national junior footballer and his friend were arrested in connection with a firing case in which a local sharebroker was seriously injured, police said on Sunday. 

Calcutta-based Abhijeet Chaterjee (24), who was studying in Vadodara and represented the U-19 national team, was arrested along with his friend Ronak Hirpara here on Saturday, they said. (PTI) 




